| -- Data for public."Course"                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
| INSERT INTO public."Course" (switch, "order", title, category, group_price, group_price_note, private_price, private_price_note, duration, description, features, button_text, button1_text, button2_text, created_at, updated_at, id) VALUES ('0', '4', 'Situational Awareness Lvl 1', 'Personal Safety', '$95', 'Group Rate', '$375', 'Private Rate', '2 Hours • Contact us to arrange a class', 'Master the art of identifying threats before they escalate with our Level 1 certification.', '"Realistic Scenarios","Practical Application","Reference Materials","Certificate of Completion"', 'Contact Us Now To Schedule', 'Contact Now', 'Group Rate', '2026-03-24T18:34:40+00:00', '2026-07-13T08:57:37.563384+00:00', '0eadc840-9fa5-4062-b9f3-04a4d1a31c33');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
| INSERT INTO public."Course" (switch, "order", title, category, group_price, group_price_note, private_price, private_price_note, duration, description, features, button_text, button1_text, button2_text, created_at, updated_at, id) VALUES ('1', '1', 'Basic Handgun Introduction', 'Handgun Basics', '$89', 'Group Rate', '$350', 'Private Rate', '4 Hours ', 'There is no live fire component to this course. There are no live firearms involved in this class. All firearms are training replicas in various forms to provide safe and accurate practical hands on familiarity.', 'Requirements for Ownership,Handgun types and actions,Handgun/Firearms Safety Rules,Shooting basics: Stance,Grip,Aiming,Trigger Control,Safe Handling and Storage,Safe and Legal Transport,Safe Use at the Range,What To Know When Visiting the Range', 'Contact Us Now To Schedule', 'Contact Now', 'Group Rate', '2026-03-24T18:34:40+00:00', '2026-07-13T08:56:40.209264+00:00', '12966d3a-bef3-4d90-8db0-3648f205afe2');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
| INSERT INTO public."Course" (switch, "order", title, category, group_price, group_price_note, private_price, private_price_note, duration, description, features, button_text, button1_text, button2_text, created_at, updated_at, id) VALUES ('0', '9', 'ETCC Emergency Tactical Casualty Control', 'Emergency Medical', '$125', 'Group Rate', '$400', 'Private Rate', '4 Hours ', 'Traumatic Bleeding Skills for Emergency Responders, Law Enforcement, Security, beyond Stop The Beed with significant hands on practice on simulated bleeding wounds. There will be simulated blood and your hands will be in it. Chest seal application practice and review of IFAK contents and requirements.', '"Traumatic bleeding intervention","For tactical or high risk situations","Beyond Stop The Bleed","Tactical or under threat considerations"', 'Contact Us Now To Schedule', 'Contact Now', 'Group Rate', '2026-03-25T21:53:23+00:00', '2026-07-13T08:58:52.04133+00:00', '2043460b-0642-4770-86bb-1ac4abbdffd6');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
| INSERT INTO public."Course" (switch, "order", title, category, group_price, group_price_note, private_price, private_price_note, duration, description, features, button_text, button1_text, button2_text, created_at, updated_at, id) VALUES ('0', '5', 'De-escalation That Works', 'Personal Safety', '$95', 'Group Rate', '$375', 'Private Rate', '2 Hours • Contact us to arrange a class', 'Learn proven verbal and non-verbal techniques to diffuse high-tension situations safely.', '"How To Go From Bad To Better","Reduce The Chance Of Violence","Practical Training","Training Materials","Certificate of Completion"', 'Contact Us Now To Schedule', 'Contact Now', 'Group Rate', '2026-03-24T18:34:40+00:00', '2026-07-13T08:58:02.263625+00:00', '223aff2a-215c-44a5-9f15-2d875a947306');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
| INSERT INTO public."Course" (switch, "order", title, category, group_price, group_price_note, private_price, private_price_note, duration, description, features, button_text, button1_text, button2_text, created_at, updated_at, id) VALUES ('1', '3', 'NJ Compliant (PTC) Permit To Carry', 'Concealed Carry', '$185', 'Group Rate', '$600', 'Private Rate', '8-10 Hours', 'This course will cover all required NJ State CCARE training requirements  as well as provide an overview of other Federal and NJ State requirements and restrictions regarding "Sensitive Places" and other information to assist you in being a safe and law abiding NJ PTC holder.

* We are training to the State approved standard and discussing State and Federal laws. However, we are not attorneys and none of this is offered as legal advice.', 'Approved CCARE Training,NJ Use of Force Training,Firearms Safety and Awareness,Federal and NJ State Law Overview,CCARE Range Qualification,Review of Application Procedures', 'Contact Us Now To Schedule', 'Contact Now', 'Group Rate', '2026-05-05T17:36:52+00:00', '2026-07-13T08:57:19.522863+00:00', '2ac68900-a07e-4a69-92ca-5c4e5fafa17f');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
| INSERT INTO public."Course" (switch, "order", title, category, group_price, group_price_note, private_price, private_price_note, duration, description, features, button_text, button1_text, button2_text, created_at, updated_at, id) VALUES ('1', '2', 'NRA Basic Pistol Shooting Certification', 'Handgun Basics', '$175', 'Group Rate', '$600', 'Private Rate', '9 Hours', 'This NRA approved course will guide you through the essentials of safely owning and operating a handgun. There is classroom with hands on learning and demonstrations of your new skills. There is also live fire training and a qualification at a local range.', 'NRA Rules For Safe Gun Handling,Pistol Types and Features,Shooting Fundamentals,Shooting Positions,Range Rules,Handgun Cleaning', 'Contact Us Now To Schedule', 'Contact Now', 'Group Rate', '2026-05-10T06:37:48+00:00', '2026-07-14T12:01:42.029472+00:00', '657227f8-095e-4cef-bad6-49d0c34ed429');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
| INSERT INTO public."Course" (switch, "order", title, category, group_price, group_price_note, private_price, private_price_note, duration, description, features, button_text, button1_text, button2_text, created_at, updated_at, id) VALUES ('1', '8', 'Stop The Bleed', 'Emergency Medical', '$55', 'Group Rate', '$250', 'Private Rate', '2 Hours • Contact us to arrange a class (Minimum 4 Attendees)', 'Life-saving training focused on rapid bleeding control and tourniquet application. Essential skills for emergency response.', '"Traumatic Bleeding First Aid","Hands On Training","Wound Packing","Tourniquet Use","Certificate of Completion"', 'Contact Us Now To Schedule', 'Contact Now', 'Group Rate', '2026-03-25T15:08:04+00:00', '2026-07-13T08:58:38.53721+00:00', '7fc94580-340b-407f-a9f2-71e032e9b2e2');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
| INSERT INTO public."Course" (switch, "order", title, category, group_price, group_price_note, private_price, private_price_note, duration, description, features, button_text, button1_text, button2_text, created_at, updated_at, id) VALUES ('1', '7', 'Conducted Energy Devices', 'Personal Defense', '$125', 'Group Rate', '$400', 'Private Rate', '3 Hours • Contact us to arrange a class', 'Introduction to conducted energy devices for civilians. Learn safety protocols, legal use, and practical application in self-defense situations.', '"Basic Safety Fundamentals","Classroom Instruction","Practice on Training Targets"," Personal Contact CED Included","Training Materials Provided","Certificate of Completion"', 'Contact Us Now To Schedule', 'Contact Now', 'Group Rate', '2026-03-25T15:08:04+00:00', '2026-07-13T08:58:25.796061+00:00', '8bd64ee7-7b08-4659-948b-19de7205c56d');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
| INSERT INTO public."Course" (switch, "order", title, category, group_price, group_price_note, private_price, private_price_note, duration, description, features, button_text, button1_text, button2_text, created_at, updated_at, id) VALUES ('0', '11', 'First Aid CPR AED', 'Emergency Medical', '$89', 'Group Rate', '$350', 'Private Rate', '4 Hours ', 'Comprehensive first aid, CPR, and AED training. Gain certification-ready skills for responding to medical emergencies.', '"HSI or AHA Certification Course","Hands-on Practical Exam","2025 Standards Compliant","Student E-Workbook Provided","Certificate and Card Provided"', 'Contact Us Now To Schedule', 'Contact Now', 'Group Rate', '2026-03-24T18:34:40+00:00', '2026-07-13T08:59:10.894788+00:00', 'a63c8e1d-d302-4880-bcdb-684289636cff');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           