| INSERT INTO public."SectionText" (id, section, field_key, field_label, field_type, value, updated_at) VALUES ('470a770f-142c-4416-b18b-08b0118af7bf', 'footer', 'legal_accessibility_content', 'Accessibility Statement Content', 'textarea', 'Accessibility Statement

Last updated: March 2026

Safe & Secure Services is committed to making our website and training programs accessible to everyone, including individuals with disabilities.
Web Accessibility

We strive to ensure our website conforms to the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1, Level AA. Our ongoing efforts include:

    Providing sufficient color contrast for all text and interactive elements.
    Ensuring all interactive elements are keyboard-navigable and have descriptive labels.
    Using semantic HTML to support screen readers and assistive technologies.
    Providing text alternatives for all non-decorative images.

In-Person Course Accommodations

We are committed to providing reasonable accommodations to course participants with disabilities. If you require an accommodation — such as large-print materials, a sign language interpreter, or accessible venue arrangements — please contact us at least 5 business days before your scheduled class so we can make appropriate arrangements.
Known Limitations

While we work continuously to improve accessibility, some older content or third-party embedded elements may not yet fully meet WCAG 2.1 AA standards. We are actively working to address these.
Feedback

We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of our website and courses. If you encounter any barriers or have suggestions, please contact us:

    Email: info@sasstac.com
    Phone: (908) 758-4894

We aim to respond to accessibility feedback within 2 business days.
', '2026-07-13T09:23:39.976594+00:00');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
